## 2. Component Library

### Location
All reusable components are in **`src/components/`**, each in its own folder with:
- `index.tsx` — Component logic
- `ComponentName.module.css` — Scoped styles

### Available Components

| Component | Path | Purpose |
|-----------|------|---------|
| `BackHeader` | `src/components/BackHeader/` | Top navigation with back arrow and optional progress bar |
| `PageHeader` | `src/components/PageHeader/` | Page title with optional subtitle |
| `PageTitle` | `src/components/PageTitle/` | Title with bold + light text variants |
| `CTAButton` | `src/components/CTAButton/` | Call-to-action button (`primary` / `secondary`) |
| `FormRow` | `src/components/FormRow/` | Input field with label |
| `ListItem` | `src/components/ListItem/` | Reusable list row with avatar/icon |
| `MenuGrid` | `src/components/MenuGrid/` | Grid layout for menu items |
| `Carousel` | `src/components/Carousel/` | Horizontal carousel slider |
| `FooterButtons` | `src/components/FooterButtons/` | Fixed bottom button area |
| `MainLayout` | `src/components/layout/MainLayout.tsx` | Main app shell with bottom nav |
| `AuthLayout` | `src/components/layout/AuthLayout.tsx` | Auth pages shell |
| `BottomNavigation` | `src/components/layout/BottomNavigation.tsx` | 5-tab bottom nav bar |

### Component Architecture Pattern

```tsx
// src/components/ComponentName/index.tsx
import styles from './ComponentName.module.css'

interface ComponentNameProps {
  // Props with TypeScript types
  text: string
  variant?: 'primary' | 'secondary'
  disabled?: boolean
  onClick?: () => void
}

function ComponentName({ text, variant = 'primary', disabled = false, onClick }: ComponentNameProps) {
  return (
    <div className={`${styles.root} ${styles[variant]}`}>
      {text}
    </div>
  )
}

export default ComponentName
```

### CTAButton Usage Example

```tsx
import CTAButton from '@components/CTAButton'

// Primary (blue filled, 360x52, rounded)
<CTAButton text="다음" onClick={handleNext} />

// Secondary (white with border)
<CTAButton text="취소" variant="secondary" onClick={handleCancel} />

// Disabled
<CTAButton text="입력해주세요" disabled />
```

**CTAButton specs (from Figma):**
- Width: 360px, Height: 52px
- Border radius: 26px (pill shape)
- Font: Pretendard 18px Bold
- Primary: `#074ED8` background, white text
- Secondary: white background, `#222222` text, `1px solid #E6E6E6` border

